-- Chile’s Hites Signs $130 Million Syndicated Loan Led by Itau
-- B y   S e b a s t i a n   B o y d
-- 2012-05-02T15:46:06Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-05-02/chile-s-hites-signs-130-million-syndicated-loan-led-by-itau.html
Empresas Hites SA (HITES) , a Santiago-based
department-store operator, agreed April 27 to borrow $130
million from a syndicate of banks led by Itau Unibanco Holding
SA’s units in Chile and New York, it said in a statement to the
Chilean securities regulator.  The company will use proceeds for investment and to
restructure its liabilities, it said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Sebastian Boyd in Santiago at 
 sboyd9@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
David Papadopoulos at 
 papadopoulos@bloomberg.net  